8208174021231619565.Text: The greater saints of the Temple, listed with their proper spheres, are: Blessed Almalexia the Warden -- Healers, Teachers, Lord Sotha Sil the Magus -- Artificers, Wizards, Lord Vivec the Poet -- Artists, Rogues, Saint Nerevar the Captain -- Warriors, Statesmen, and Saint Veloth the Pilgrim -- Outcasts, Seekers.
